#: ../../quickstart.md:1
msgid "Quickstart"
msgstr "Démarrage rapide"

#: ../../quickstart.md:3
msgid "This page takes you from `pip install` to your first narrated game turn."
msgstr "Cette page vous emmène du `pip install` à votre premier tour de jeu narré."

#: ../../quickstart.md:5
msgid "Requirements"
msgstr "Prérequis"

#: ../../quickstart.md:7
msgid "**Python 3.11 or newer.**"
msgstr "**Python 3.11 ou plus récent.**"

#: ../../quickstart.md:8
msgid ""
"An LLM you can call: either a **Google Gemini API key** (free tier works) or"
" any **OpenAI-compatible endpoint** — a local [Ollama](https://ollama.com) "
"server, LM Studio, llama.cpp, vLLM…"
msgstr ""
"Un LLM que vous pouvez appeler : soit une **clé API Google Gemini** (le "
"palier gratuit suffit), soit n'importe quel **endpoint compatible OpenAI** —"
" un serveur [Ollama](https://ollama.com) local, LM Studio, llama.cpp, vLLM…"

#: ../../quickstart.md:12
msgid "Install"
msgstr "Installation"

#: ../../quickstart.md:18
msgid ""
"This installs the `axiom` Python package and the `axiom` command-line tool. "
"Check it works:"
msgstr ""
"Cela installe le paquet Python `axiom` et l'outil en ligne de commande "
"`axiom`. Vérifiez que tout fonctionne :"

#: ../../quickstart.md:26
msgid "`axiom.help()` prints a short usage guide right in the REPL."
msgstr "`axiom.help()` affiche un petit guide d'utilisation directement dans le REPL."

#: ../../quickstart.md:28
msgid "Configure an LLM backend"
msgstr "Configurer un backend LLM"

#: ../../quickstart.md:30
msgid ""
"The engine reads its configuration from `~/.config/AxiomAI/settings.json` "
